CCMO_COLLAT_ASSUMPTIONS Struct Reference

This structure is passed to the per-collateral assumptions call back function. Populate its element with assumptions for all amortization periods. For use of the per collateral assumptions call back function, populate assumptions for a given collateral for the entire simulation period. More...

#include <ccmo.h>

Field Documentation

double* CCMO_COLLAT_ASSUMPTIONS::prepay_vector

Vector of prepayment values. It should be populated starting from element 1. The size of the vector does not exceeds MAX_PERIODS. Numbers should be provided in decimals. The last value will be propagated to the end of simulation.
